            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Hic requiiscet <note>sic</note> in pace Alvia <note>sic</note> quae vixit <lb n="2"/>annos novem et <expan><abbr>sep</abbr><ex>ulta</ex></expan><certainty match="preceding-sibling::node()" locus="value"/> e&amp;lt;s<certainty match="preceding-sibling::node()" locus="value"/>&amp;gt;t cum Luciano <expan><abbr>h</abbr><ex>onestae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>emoriae</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/>avo suo et deposi<supplied reason="lost">t</supplied>a est sub <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>ie</ex></expan> X Ka<supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>endas</ex></expan></supplied> <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>Decembr</abbr><ex>es</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>d<am>d</am></abbr><ex>ominis</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>n<am>n</am></abbr><ex>ostris</ex></expan> Th<supplied reason="lost">eo</supplied>dosio XV et <supplied reason="lost">Pla</supplied><lb break="no" n="5"/>cido Valentinia<supplied reason="lost">no IIII <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>er</ex><abbr>p</abbr><ex>etuis</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Augg</abbr><ex>ustis</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>cons</abbr><ex>ulibus</ex></expan></supplied>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Zwei aneinanderpassende Fragmente von der Vorderseite eines Sarkophagkastens; ein Teil des rechten Fragments inzwischen verschollen. Z. 2: statt sep(ulta) e&amp;lt;s&amp;gt;t möglicherweise auch sedet. Z. 5: die Zeile war bei der Auffindung noch fast vollständig erhalten. (B): CIL III 2657; CIL III 2657 add. p. 1032; CIL III 13962; ILCV: Abweichungen in Lesung / Ergänzung.</p>
            </div>
